Introduction

NINE to SIX (Korean: 나인투식스; Japanese: 9時から6時まで) is the second sub-unit of the boy group DKZ under Dongyo Entertainment. The sub-unit consists of two members: Mingyu and Jonghyeong. They made their official debut on May 31, 2023 with the single album "Good to You."
